# ============================================================================
# Vianigram .gitignore
# Cubre: soluciĂłn VS (managed C# WP8.1 + native C++/CX/WinRT), packaging UWP,
# tooling .NET (tl-codegen) y archivos locales/sensibles.
# ============================================================================

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Telegram app credentials (api_id / api_hash) â€” NEVER commit real values.
# Real credentials live in *.Local.cs which is gitignored; the committed
# *.cs ships with placeholders. See TelegramAppConfig.Local.cs.example.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/TelegramAppConfig.Local.cs
**/*.Local.cs

